++  change-nicks                                        ::<  change nick map
  ::>  changes a nickname in a map, adding if it doesn't
  ::>  yet exist, removing if the nickname is empty.
  ::
  |=  {nis/(map ship cord) who/ship nic/cord}
  ^+  nis
  ?:  =(nic '')
    (~(del by nis) who)
  (~(put by nis) who nic)
